data.description: All new interior paint, neutral, not blue as pics show! Place this home at the TOP of your list to see today! OH SO SPACIOUS 5 bedroom / 3 bath with an absolutely incredible fenced back yard. Plenty of room for a pool and there is already an aviary/pet pen also! Pair all of these comforts with a brand-new roof to boot. This family-friendly floor plan (that's a tongue twister) affords TWO primary bedrooms with en suite bathrooms, plus three more bedrooms and a guest bath as well. Envision an evening sitting outside on the expansive screened lanai watching the sunset or enjoying the children and the furbabies playing! This floor plan also boasts an inside laundry room, freshly painted garage, and SO MUCH living space. Make this a great next step home or forever home for your family!
